title: Abdul Hanif of PML(N) wins PP-17 Rawalpindi
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Abdul Hanif of Pakistan Muslim League(N) won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-17 Rawalpindi by securing 45677 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Raja Rashid Hafeez, an independent candidate who bagged 38189 votes.
Votersâ€™ turnout remained at 41.14 per cent.
